---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Work Together">
  <section class="py-20 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6">Work Together</div>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl text-text-main mb-8">Let's build the thing your AI strategy is <em class="text-accent italic">quietly missing.</em></h1>
    <p class="font-serif text-2xl text-text-muted italic max-w-2xl mb-16">
      Not a deck. Not a workshop. The actual operational machinery that keeps your AI paying off as the company changes.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-24">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-text-main mb-12">Five shapes an engagement tends to take:</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-0">
        <div class="py-10 border-t border-base-light grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_200px] gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-text-main mb-4">The <em class="text-accent italic">reckoning</em></h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">A clear-eyed look at what you've actually deployed, what's coming for you regulatorily, and what the gap is between those two things. No judgment, no panic.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:border-l md:border-base-light md:pl-8">
            <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-1">Time</div>
            <div class="font-serif text-xl text-primary mb-4">4–6 weeks</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-1">Shape</div>
            <div class="font-serif text-xl text-primary">Assessment</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="py-10 border-t border-base-light grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_200px] gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-text-main mb-4">The <em class="text-accent italic">scaffolding</em></h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Governance structures, policies, risk classification, documentation architecture, human oversight mechanisms, audit trails. The invisible infrastructure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:border-l md:border-base-light md:pl-8">
            <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-1">Time</div>
            <div class="font-serif text-xl text-primary mb-4">8–12 weeks</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-1">Shape</div>
            <div class="font-serif text-xl text-primary">Build</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="py-10 border-t border-base-light grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_200px] gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-text-main mb-4">The <em class="text-accent italic">translation</em></h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">You're a fintech with real regulatory operations already in place. You need those same muscles pointed at AI without breaking what already works.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:border-l md:border-base-light md:pl-8">
            <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-1">Time</div>
            <div class="font-serif text-xl text-primary mb-4">6–10 weeks</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-1">Shape</div>
            <div class="font-serif text-xl text-primary">Extension</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>